    German (de) — the TOKEN second culture. Deliberately a small subset: enough that switching the language is
    visibly, demonstrably working end to end (nav, layout, login, dashboard headings), not a full translation.

    Every key NOT listed here falls back to the English value in SharedResource.resx. That fallback is the whole
    point: a culture can be shipped partial and grown over time, and importing a full translation later
    (Chinese, French, …) means dropping in SharedResource.<culture>.resx with the same keys — no code change.
  -->
